This paper is likely to belong to the Graphics (cs.GR) sub-category as it focuses on simulating small-scale liquid flows for animation. Additionally, the use of deep neural networks for prediction and simulation suggests that it could also belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-categories.
